{"tid":1749470,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"沙田區禾輋村余倩文拉票","createTime":"2019-11-24T03:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T22:18:19.000Z","uid":86392,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9a7852db8d3ce9d978a287c82b720cbb701bc13a","tid":1749470,"uid":86392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"條8婆係票站範圍拉票，沙田柚一齊投訴佢。<br />\n <br />\n電話: 2827 7251<br />\nemail: reoenq@reo.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\nTemplate:<br />\n<br />\n選舉管理委員會<br />\n公關部主任﹕<br />\n　　本人在二零一九年十一月二十四日在沙田禾輋村商場票站時，發現余債雯在票站範圍公然拉票，多名市民或選站職員屢勸不止。本人為此感到十分氣憤，固寫信來投訴。<br />\n　　當日早上約11時15分，本人排隊進入票站時，余倩雯從票站走出，並公然拉票：辛苦晒/ 多謝支持，並和選民握手言歡。當本人引用選舉委員會之條例以勸告余倩雯離開時，並無即時離開，而是慢步環繞人隊一圈，視作抗議。<br />\n　　我們大家都感到十分憤憤不平 。<br />\n　　選舉委員會一向印象十分良好，職員亦盡心盡責。可是，這次事件令我十分失望。<br />\n　　希望委員會能為今次事件解釋，並對余倩雯之行為作出懲罰，以儆效尤。<br />\n<br />\n選民<br />\nXXX<br />\n二零一九年十一月二十四日"},{"pid":"2ee1157de20325bd77af33b0d73b67293e80c74f","tid":1749470,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xesye2H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXesye2H.jpg&h=49fac974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住要影相"},{"pid":"9ae4d456bd243642d997234ed87096d4aa6c7a2b","tid":1749470,"uid":86392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ee1157de20325bd77af33b0d73b67293e80c74f","tid":1749470,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xesye2H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXesye2H.jpg&h=49fac974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住要影相"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:55:11.000Z","msg":"up唔到相，有無ching教路？"},{"pid":"725275ef1caf61fbe717bc49a3c0d78da8cb681f","tid":1749470,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:57:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1a2f3fbded5e7e5e89bd380ed0bdd25f3d346ab","tid":1749470,"uid":86392,"like":0